{"tid":365190,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"拜仁主席：如果丹比利罷訓真係巴塞搞鬼 我唔會再尊重巴塞","createTime":"2017-08-19T04:53:34.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-19T11:10:02.000Z","uid":10338,"like":57,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4ca03310d95796da182e1cc909abbe565c56cfd1","tid":365190,"uid":10338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T04:53:34.000Z","msg":"拜仁慕尼黑主席漢尼斯日前在接受采訪的時候，批評了多蒙特球星丹比利通過罷訓來謀求轉會的愚蠢行為。<br />\n在接受采訪的時候，漢尼斯說道：&ldquo;球員不來參加訓練，這是最最低級的手段，而如果巴塞真的在這種行為背後扮演著什麼角色，那我對於這傢球會的尊重也就蕩然無存了。&rdquo;<br />\n對於如果拜仁球員做出類似丹比利行為的後果，漢尼斯表示：&ldquo;如果有球員敢干這種事，他每天收到的罰金將會是10萬歐。&rdquo;<br />\n漢尼斯繼續說道：&ldquo;如果多蒙特能夠通過轉會得到1.2、1.3或者1.5億轉會費，那多蒙特才是贏家，球員並不是，當然不能讓球員來主導轉會價格。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n連仁哥d手下都敢郁<br />\n巴塞真係得罪全歐洲"},{"pid":"1fb283fbc45cbf40d50268e4c97236f965d7b816","tid":365190,"uid":36287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T04:54:24.000Z","msg":"高層<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a66d70fbde4f5dc6a9b2f25bb859d7e5bc7fb5f","tid":365190,"uid":760,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T04:54:49.000Z","msg":"算數喇拜仁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a656fbbbce960d960d57dce4a83c67e35248e2c1","tid":365190,"uid":3369,"like":51,"dislike":0,"score":51,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T04:54:59.000Z","msg":"疤狗買左既話，拜狗仲點撚樣免簽啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4835eb10741c16c9550f571127f72bc06332d67d","tid":365190,"uid":5763,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T04:55:37.000Z","msg":"多仔D野關你撚事咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c54a1de76db28c912053bef39a3315f04da6b3c","tid":365190,"uid":40938,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T04:56:36.000Z","msg":"爭住出黎做保長<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src